---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Stability — The Key to Grow Confidently | Case Study"
  description="How Cable Analytics used HedgeFlows to reduce currency risks stemming from the drop of the pound against the dollar."
>
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav class="mb-8 text-[0.875rem] text-text-muted">
        <a href="/case-studies" class="hover:text-brand-green transition-colors">Case Studies</a>
        <span class="mx-2">/</span>
        <span class="text-text-heading font-medium">Cable Analytics</span>
      </nav>

      <!-- Tags -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-brand-green-pale text-brand-green text-[0.8125rem] font-semibold rounded-full">
          Startups & Scaleups
        </span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-text-muted text-[0.8125rem] font-medium rounded-full">
          Risk Management
        </span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-[2rem] md:text-[2.5rem] font-bold text-text-heading leading-tight mb-4">
        Stability — the key to remain competitive and achieve growth
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[1.25rem] text-brand-green font-semibold mb-10">Cable Analytics</p>

      <!-- Pull Quote -->
      <blockquote class="my-10 p-8 bg-brand-green-pale rounded-xl border-l-4 border-brand-green">
        <p class="text-[1.125rem] text-text-heading leading-relaxed italic">
          &ldquo;We were using Western Union for our spot transactions before, but getting support was impossible. HedgeFlows is much more competitive and give us the stability we need. Whenever we need support, we get it straightaway.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <cite class="block mt-4 text-[0.9375rem] text-text-body not-italic font-medium">
          &mdash; Davy, Co-founder
        </cite>
      </blockquote>

      <!-- Content Sections -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE COMPANY</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          Professional communications test and measurement
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p>Cable Analytics Limited are a UK based distributor of professional communications test and measurement instruments serving the data and telecommunications market.</p>
<p>The founders, Davy and Eddie, have a strong vision &mdash; to provide equal service to both distributors and their clients. They aim to disrupt the UK market and achieve a 25% market share within the next 12–18 months.</p>
        </div>
        <figure class="mt-6">
          <img src="https://8698300.hs-sites.com/hs-fs/hubfs/cable%20analytics.jpg?width=700&name=cable%20analytics.jpg" alt="The Cable Analytics team" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-sm" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption class="mt-2 text-[0.8125rem] text-text-muted text-center">The Cable Analytics team</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE PROBLEM</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          The drop of the pound
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p>The economic situation and the position of the Dollar ($) against the Pound (£) have been a concern for both Eddie and Davy in the last couple of months.</p>
<p>A friend recommended HedgeFlows saying it was simple and easy to use. Flexibility and stability are the main reasons why the team now rely on HedgeFlows.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE SOLUTION</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          A flexible solution
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p>Booking exchange rates in advance with HedgeFlows provides the stability Cable Analytics need to remain competitive. As Davy and Eddie prepare their purchase orders, they use HedgeFlows to track exchange rates automatically. When rates reach their target, they can easily book the guaranteed exchange in advance without having to block any cash.</p>
<p>A few weeks or months later, they use the booked Dollar rate to pay the invoices.</p>
        </div>
        <figure class="mt-6">
          <img src="https://8698300.hs-sites.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Rateslevel.png?width=500&name=Rateslevel.png" alt="HedgeFlows rate tracking" class="mx-auto rounded-xl shadow-sm max-w-[280px]" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption class="mt-2 text-[0.8125rem] text-text-muted text-center">Track rates and book in advance with HedgeFlows</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE IMPACT</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          Prebooking dollars to remain competitive
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p><strong>Securing the right exchange rate</strong> &mdash; The drop in the Pound could have potentially hurt them, but they had the option to hedge a previous rate. The HedgeFlows team was very supportive even after terms expired, providing the flexibility and assistance to help them through tough periods.</p>
<p><strong>Saving money and remaining competitive</strong> &mdash; The team at Cable Analytics has saved a total of £3,500 so far by prebooking their exchange rates up to 12 months in advance. Some extra cash they can now use to promote their business.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <blockquote class="my-8 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-gray-200">
        <p class="text-[1rem] text-text-body leading-relaxed italic">
          &ldquo;The drop in the Pound could have potentially hurt us, but we had the option to hedge a previous rate. The guys at HedgeFlows have been very good at helping us even after the terms were expired. Having that flexibility and that assistance to help us through that tough period has helped us remain competitive.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <cite class="block mt-3 text-[0.875rem] text-text-muted not-italic font-medium">
          &mdash; Davy, Co-founder
        </cite>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-green font-semibold hover:gap-3 transition-all">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
          Back to case studies
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    headline="Want similar results for your business?"
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Book a Treasury Review', href: '/treasury-health-check' }}
  />
</PageLayout>
